  "narrative": {
    "text": "Switzerland is a Europe and Central Asia country with a DB-type pension system centred on the Old Age and Survivors Insurance (AHV/AVS) \u2013 DB Earnings-Related. The system includes 2 schemes: Old Age and Survivors Insurance (AHV/AVS) \u2013 DB Earnings-Related, Occupational Pension (BVG/LPP) \u2013 Mandatory. The normal retirement age is 65 for men and 64 for women. Contributions total 11.0% of insurable earnings (5.5% employee, 5.5% employer).",
